<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Tradeboard</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu,
          Cantarell, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f5f5f7;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a073f0 0%, #8a5cf5 100%);
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 180px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: white;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 32px;
      }

      .welcome-message,
      .role-section {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      .welcome-message p,
      .role-section p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #1d1d1f;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .name {
        color: #a073f0;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

.button {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #a073f0;
  color: white; /* <-- ensures white text */
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 12px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin: 24px 0;
  transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.button:hover {
  background: #8a5cf5;
  color: white; /* <-- keeps text white on hover */
}


      .info-box {
        padding: 24px;
        background: #f8f5ff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border-left: 4px solid #a073f0;
        margin: 32px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #1d1d1f;
      }

      .info-box ul {
        margin: 12px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      .info-box li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .support-message {
        padding: 24px;
        background: #fff8e1;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        margin: 32px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #1d1d1f;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px;
        background: #f5f5f7;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #86868b;
      }

      /* Animation for container */
      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      .animate {
        animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 20px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 24px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 24px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container animate">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://test.tradeboard.in/images/Tradeboard_logo_RGB.png"
          alt="Tradeboard Logo"
          class="logo"
        />
        <h1>Welcome to Tradeboard</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <div class="welcome-message">
          <p>Hello {{partnerName}},</p>
          <p>You have been added as an accountability partner for
            <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>
            in their trading journey with Tradeboard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="role-section">
          <p>As an accountability partner, you can view
            <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>'s current month's trading
            performance anytime by clicking the button below. The dashboard will
            always show the most recent month's data whenever you access it.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">View Trading Dashboard</a>
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <p><strong>What you can do:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>View current month's trading performance (Sunday to Saturday)</li>
            <li>Track progress across multiple metrics</li>
            <li>Access the dashboard anytime using the link above</li>
            <li>Support and encourage
              <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>
              in their trading goals</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Your role as an accountability partner is crucial in helping traders
          stay motivated and disciplined. We appreciate your commitment to
          supporting
          <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>.</p>

        <div class="support-message">
          <p><strong>Important:</strong>
            You cannot make any changes to
            <span class="name">{{userName}}</span>'s data or account. You have
            view-only access to help provide support and accountability.</p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="support-message"
          style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left-color: #2196f3;"
        >
          <p>If you have any questions about your role or need assistance,
            please don't hesitate to reach out to us at
            <a
              href="mailto:contactus@tradeboard.in"
              style="color: #2196f3;"
            >contactus@tradeboard.in</a></p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Thank you for being a part of the
            Tradeboard community!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>